# Normalize line endings across platforms so build outputs (tsc, webpack)
# don't produce persistent CRLF-vs-LF diffs on Windows checkouts.
#
# * text=auto eol=lf — git stores all detected text files with LF and
# checks them out as LF, ignoring core.autocrlf. Binary files are left
# untouched by detection.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit overrides for Windows-native scripts that really do need CRLF.
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf

# Common binary extensions in this repo — mark so Git never attempts
# text conversion on them.
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.gif binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.mp3 binary
*.wav binary
*.ogg binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.pdf binary
